data.description: "Contract pending inspection period" Situated in the heart of Lincoln, Nebraska, this home likely offers convenience to amenities, shops, and possibly local attractions. A two-story design offers ample living space with two bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing comfort and functionality. The wood floors on the main level add warmth and character to the home, while the galley kitchen and dinning room with a bay window offers plenty of natural light and a cozy atmosphere. The minimal yard requires lower maintenance, making it ideal for those who prefer to spend less time on yard work. The deck out back provides space for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. An unfinished basement offers potential for future living space, which could be customized to suit the homeowner's needs and preferences. The inclusion of laundry facilities and a second bathroom in the basement adds practicality and convenience.
